snippet.title: Nailed It! Baking Bash | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Play Nailed It! Baking Bash on your mobile devices. Coming soon exclusively on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81517264

Calling all home bakers! Host a party for your pals to see who creates the best-looking – or worst-looking – cakes in this game based on the hit series.

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/29qBUt7

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services with 233 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
